      • calculateFee

        public float calculateFee(float coefficient)
        Calculate Parking Fee
        参数:
        coefficient - Parking fee coefficient. By default, we set it to 5 in PCS.cfg file Fee is calculated by second for easy demo If there is no PayMachine set,which means this ticket isn't paid, so calculate the fee by time If there is already a PayMachine ID here, which means the driver paid, then the fee is 0 Update the parkingFee
        返回:
        return parking fee

      • setPayMachineID

        public boolean valid(java.util.logging.Logger log,
                     java.lang.String id)

        返回:

      • setExitInformation

      • setExitInformationTmp

        public void setExitInformationTmp(long exitTimeCoefficientTmp,
                                  java.lang.String payMachineIDTmp,
                                  float parkingFeeTmp)
        Store Tmp value when insert the ticket
        参数:
        exitTimeCoefficientTmp - used to calculate exitTime=currentTime+exitTimeCoefficient Set exitTime=exitTimeTmp when Oct Pay
        payMachineIDTmp - set payMachine ID. Set payMachineID=payMachineIDTmp when Oct Pay
        parkingFeeTmp - calculated Parking fee. Set parkingFee=parkingFeeTmp when Oct Pay
